'''Akomeye mu mutwe'''

Umuntu yitwa ko akomeye mu mutwe igihe ashobora gukora neza mu buzima bwa minsi yose, agakorana n’abandi, agafata ingingo, akagira ico aterera mu kibano, akamenya ingene yigenza mu bintu bigusagirije no mu bihe bigoye, akongera agashika kukunezerwa bikwiye. Indwara zo mu mutwe n’indwara zihungabanya amagara y’umuntu mu mutwe.

Impunzi zirakunda gufatwa n’indwara zo mu mutwe kubera ivyo zaciyemwo mu buzima bihahamura. Igihugu c’amavuko cabo kenshi kirakenye kandi nta mutekano ukiranga, bashobora kuba barahungabanirijwe ubuzima, barabuze canke barazimije ababo, canke bapfunzwe.

== Ubwoko bwinshi bw’indwara zo mu mutwe ==
Hari ubwoko bwinshi bw’indwara zo mu mutwe, hakaba n’uburyo bwinshi bwo kuzivura. Kwihebura ukaguma wijiriwe niyo ndwara yo mu mutwe ikunda kuboneka. Izindi ni :

Guhahamuka (PTSD). Ivyo bishora gushika igihe umuntu yagize ubwoba cane canke yahwanye n’ingorane zimutera ubwoba cane, nko gukubitwa, guhwana n’isanganya ry’icaduka, guterwa n’abashimutsi, canke indwano za gisirikare. Abantu bahahamutse baguma bibuka ivyabaye, bakarara bararota ibiteye ubwoba, canke bigatuma bahwana n’ibisubira kubahahamura. Bashobora kwadukana ishavu canke bakiyotsa rwose ibibi boba barakoze, ubwoba, n’ibindi. Ukwo guhahamuka (PTSD) kurashobora kubera intambanyi ubuzima bw’umuntu bwa minsi yose.

